---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { client } from "../../client.config.js";

// ===== SHARED BLOG POST DATA =====
// Keep this synchronized with the blog index page
export const localPosts = [
  {
    title:
      "Small Garden, Big Impact Maximizing Space with Creative Landscaping",
    excerpt:
      "Discover how to transform even the smallest outdoor spaces into breathtaking sanctuaries using vertical gardens and multi-functional features.",
    date: "September 4, 2024",
    category: "Design",
    author: "James Miller",
    image: "/images/blog/spring-tips.png",
    slug: "spring-landscaping-tips",
    content: `
      <p>Professional garden landscaping provides a multitude of benefits that go beyond mere aesthetics. By enhancing your outdoor space, it not only boosts curb appeal but also significantly increases your property value.</p>
      <blockquote class="ref-quote">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M14.017 21L14.017 18C14.017 16.8954 14.9124 16 16.017 16H19.017C19.5693 16 20.017 15.5523 20.017 15V9C20.017 8.44772 19.5693 8 19.017 8H15.017C14.4647 8 14.017 8.44772 14.017 9V15M3 21L3 18C3 16.8954 3.89543 16 5 16H8C8.55228 16 9 15.5523 9 15V9C9 8.44772 8.55228 8 8 8H4C3.44772 8 3 8.44772 3 9V15"/></svg>
        Experience the Full Range of Benefits with Professional Garden Landscaping: From Boosting Property Value to Creating a Beautiful, Functional, and Sustainable Outdoor Oasis.
      </blockquote>
      <p>Expert landscapers design functional, aesthetically pleasing spaces that maximize your garden's potential, incorporating sustainable practices and plant selections tailored to your environment.</p>
      <h2 class="post-subheading">Elevate Your Garden with Professionals</h2>
      <ul class="post-list">
        <li>Enhanced Aesthetic Appeal</li>
        <li>Increased Property Value</li>
        <li>Functional Outdoor Spaces</li>
        <li>Time and Effort Savings</li>
      </ul>
    `,
  },
  {
    title: "Sustainable Gardening Eco-Friendly Landscaping Ideas",
    excerpt:
      "Learn the principles of ecological design and how to create a garden that thrives with minimal resources while supporting local biodiversity.",
    date: "September 4, 2024",
    category: "Sustainability",
    author: "James Miller",
    image: "/images/blog/drought-tolerant.png",
    slug: "drought-tolerant-gardens",
    content: `
      <p>Sustainable gardening is the future of landscaping. By choosing native plants and implementing water-saving techniques, you can create a beautiful garden that respects the local ecosystem.</p>
      <h2 class="post-subheading">Eco-Friendly Strategies</h2>
      <p>Using drought-tolerant species and organic fertilizers reduces the environmental impact of your garden while lowering maintenance costs.</p>
      <ul class="post-list">
        <li>Native Plant Selection</li>
        <li>Drip Irrigation Systems</li>
        <li>Organic Pest Management</li>
        <li>Composting and Soil Health</li>
      </ul>
    `,
  },
  {
    title: "Water Features Adding Serenity to Your Garden",
    excerpt:
      "From minimalist ponds to architectural waterfalls, explore how water elements can enhance the peace and tranquility of your landscape.",
    date: "September 4, 2024",
    category: "Design",
    author: "James Miller",
    image: "/images/blog/lighting-trends.png",
    slug: "outdoor-lighting-trends",
    content: `
      <p>The sound of running water can transform any garden into a peaceful retreat. Water features add a dynamic element to your landscape, attracting wildlife and masking neighborhood noise.</p>
      <h2 class="post-subheading">Choosing the Right Feature</h2>
      <p>Whether it's a simple birdbath or a complex waterfall, the key is to integrate the feature seamlessly with your existing plants and hardscape.</p>
      <ul class="post-list">
        <li>Minimalist Ponds</li>
        <li>Architectural Waterfalls</li>
        <li>Interactive Fountains</li>
        <li>Reflecting Pools</li>
      </ul>
    `,
  },
  {
    title: "The Benefits of Professional Garden Landscaping",
    excerpt:
      "Why hiring a professional designer is an investment that pays off in both property value and personal wellbeing.",
    date: "September 4, 2024",
    category: "Professional",
    author: "James Miller",
    image: "/images/service-1.png",
    slug: "professional-benefits",
    content: `
      <p>Professional landscaping is more than just planting flowers. it's a strategic investment in your home's future and your daily quality of life.</p>
      <h2 class="post-subheading">Why Go Professional?</h2>
      <p>A professional designer understands the long-term growth patterns of plants and how to create a balanced, year-round aesthetic.</p>
      <ul class="post-list">
        <li>Strategic Design Planning</li>
        <li>Expert Plant Selection</li>
        <li>Professional Installation</li>
        <li>Long-term Maintenance</li>
      </ul>
    `,
  },
  {
    title: "Revamp Your Garden Latest Landscaping Trends for 2024",
    excerpt:
      "Stay ahead of the curve with our curated list of the most exciting design trends shaping the world of modern landscaping this year.",
    date: "September 4, 2024",
    category: "Trends",
    author: "James Miller",
    image: "/images/service-2.png",
    slug: "trends-2024",
    content: `
      <p>2024 is all about blending the indoors with the outdoors. We're seeing a rise in outdoor kitchens, fire pits, and comfortable lounge areas that feel like true extensions of the home.</p>
      <h2 class="post-subheading">Modern Trends to Watch</h2>
      <ul class="post-list">
        <li>Biophilic Design Elements</li>
        <li>Smart Irrigation Tech</li>
        <li>Dark Hardscaping Tones</li>
        <li>Pollinator-Friendly Gardens</li>
      </ul>
    `,
  },
  {
    title: "Garden Landscaping Innovations What's New in Outdoor Design",
    excerpt:
      "Exploring the cutting-edge materials and technologies that are redefining how we interact with our outdoor environments.",
    date: "September 4, 2024",
    category: "Innovation",
    author: "James Miller",
    image: "/images/service-3.png",
    slug: "innovations",
    content: `
      <p>Innovation in landscaping is moving fast. From permeable pavers that manage runoff to sustainable lighting solutions, the possibilities for your garden are endless.</p>
      <h2 class="post-subheading">Cutting-Edge Tech</h2>
      <p>New materials and automated systems are making it easier than ever to maintain a high-end landscape with minimal effort.</p>
      <ul class="post-list">
        <li>Permeable Hardscaping</li>
        <li>Solar Powered Lighting</li>
        <li>Automated Mowing Systems</li>
        <li>Vertical Living Walls</li>
      </ul>
    `,
  },
];

// ===== GENERATE STATIC PATHS =====
export async function getStaticPaths() {
  return localPosts.map((post) => ({
    params: { slug: post.slug },
  }));
}

// ===== PAGE LOGIC =====
const { slug } = Astro.params;

// Find the post by slug
const post = localPosts.find((p) => p.slug === slug);

// Fallback to first post if not found (prevents crashes)
const displayPost = post || localPosts[0];

// Log warning if post not found (helps with debugging)
if (!post && import.meta.env.DEV) {
  console.warn(`⚠️  Blog post not found for slug: "${slug}"`);
  console.warn(
    `📝 Available slugs:`,
    localPosts.map((p) => p.slug),
  );
}

const primary = (client.primaryColor || "#b45309").trim();
---

<Layout
  title={displayPost.title}
  description={`Read more about ${displayPost.title}`}
>
  <!-- Individual Blog Hero -->
  <section class="post-hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img src="/images/blog-hero.png" alt={displayPost.title} />
      <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content-inner">
        <h1>{displayPost.title}</h1>
        <div class="post-meta-row">
          <span class="meta-item">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="18"
              height="18"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"
              ></rect><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line><line
                x1="8"
                y1="2"
                x2="8"
                y2="6"></line><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line></svg
            >
            {displayPost.date}
          </span>
          <span class="meta-item">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="18"
              height="18"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><path
                d="M20.59 13.41l-7.17 7.17a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0L2 12V2h10l8.59 8.59a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.82z"
              ></path><line x1="7" y1="7" x2="7.01" y2="7"></line></svg
            >
            Per {displayPost.category}
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Post Main Section -->
  <section class="post-body-section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <!-- Featured Image -->
      <div class="post-img-box">
        <img src={displayPost.image} alt={displayPost.title} />
      </div>

      <!-- Article Content -->
      <div class="post-content-inner" set:html={displayPost.content} />

      <!-- Post Footer (Tags & Share) -->
      <div class="post-footer-row">
        <div class="footer-left">
          <span class="footer-label">Tags:</span>
          <div class="pill-tags">
            <span class="pill-tag">Physiscare</span>
            <span class="pill-tag">Wellness</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-right">
          <div class="social-pills">
            <a href="#" class="social-pill"
              ><svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="18"
                height="18"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="currentColor"
                ><path
                  d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"
                ></path></svg
              ></a
            >
            <a href="#" class="social-pill"
              ><svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="18"
                height="18"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="currentColor"
                ><path
                  d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"
                ></path></svg
              ></a
            >
            <a href="#" class="social-pill"
              ><svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="18"
                height="18"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="currentColor"
                ><path
                  d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"
                ></path><rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"></rect><circle
                  cx="4"
                  cy="4"
                  r="2"></circle></svg
              ></a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Comment Form -->
      <div class="comment-area">
        <h3 class="area-title">Leave a Reply</h3>
        <p class="area-desc">
          Your email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *
        </p>

        <form class="luxe-form">
          <div class="form-item full">
            <textarea placeholder="Comment *" rows="6"></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="form-grid-3">
            <div class="form-item">
              <input type="text" placeholder="Name *" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-item">
              <input type="email" placeholder="Email *" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-item">
              <input type="text" placeholder="Website" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check">
            <input type="checkbox" id="save-cookies" />
            <label for="save-cookies"
              >Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next
              time I comment.</label
            >
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="luxe-submit-btn">Post Comment</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Grass Silhouette Divider -->
  <div class="grass-divider">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path
        d="M0,100 L0,20 L10,0 L20,30 L30,5 L40,25 L50,15 L60,40 L70,10 L80,30 L90,20 L100,50 L110,15 L120,35 L130,25 L140,45 L150,10 L160,30 L170,20 L180,40 L190,15 L200,35 L210,25 L220,45 L230,10 L240,30 L250,20 L260,40 L270,15 L280,35 L290,25 L300,45 L310,10 L320,30 L330,20 L340,40 L350,15 L360,35 L370,25 L380,45 L390,10 L400,30 L410,20 L420,40 L430,15 L440,35 L450,25 L460,45 L470,10 L480,30 L490,20 L500,40 L510,15 L520,35 L530,25 L540,45 L550,10 L560,30 L570,20 L580,40 L590,15 L600,35 L610,25 L620,45 L630,10 L640,30 L650,20 L660,40 L670,15 L680,35 L690,25 L700,45 L710,10 L720,30 L730,20 L740,40 L750,15 L760,35 L770,25 L780,45 L790,10 L800,30 L810,20 L820,40 L830,15 L840,35 L850,25 L860,45 L870,10 L880,30 L890,20 L900,40 L910,15 L920,35 L930,25 L940,45 L950,10 L960,30 L970,20 L980,40 L990,15 L1000,35 L1010,25 L1020,45 L1030,10 L1040,30 L1050,20 L1060,40 L1070,15 L1080,35 L1090,25 L1100,45 L1110,10 L1120,30 L1130,20 L1140,40 L1150,15 L1160,35 L1170,25 L1180,45 L1190,10 L1200,30 L1200,100 Z"
        fill="#b45309"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <style define:vars={{ primary }}>
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .container-narrow {
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    /* Post Hero */
    .post-hero {
      height: 450px;
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .hero-bg img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
    }

    .hero-content-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    .hero-content-inner h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }

    .post-meta-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .meta-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .meta-item svg {
      color: #fff;
    }

    /* Post Body Section */
    .post-body-section {
      padding: 80px 0;
      background: #f8f1ec;
    }

    .post-img-box {
      margin-bottom: 50px;
      border-radius: 32px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    .post-img-box img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .post-content-inner {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #333;
    }

    .post-content-inner :global(p) {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .post-content-inner :global(.post-subheading) {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #111;
      margin: 60px 0 30px;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .post-content-inner :global(.post-list) {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .post-content-inner :global(.post-list li) {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      position: relative;
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 35px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .post-content-inner :global(.post-list li::before) {
      content: "•";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: #b45309;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .post-content-inner :global(.ref-quote) {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 50px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      margin: 60px 0;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #b45309;
      line-height: 1.6;
      position: relative;
      border-left: 12px solid #b45309;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
    }

    .post-content-inner :global(.ref-quote svg) {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      color: #b45309;
      opacity: 0.2;
    }

    /* Post Footer Row */
    .post-footer-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 50px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      margin-top: 60px;
    }

    .footer-left {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .footer-label {
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #111;
    }

    .pill-tags {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .pill-tag {
      background: #b45309;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 24px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .social-pills {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .social-pill {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      background: #b45309;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 50%;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .social-pill:hover {
      background: #b45309;
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    /* Comment Area */
    .comment-area {
      margin-top: 100px;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 70px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .area-title {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #111;
    }

    .area-desc {
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .luxe-form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 25px;
    }

    .form-item textarea,
    .form-item input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 20px 25px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      background: #f1f8f3;
      font-size: 1rem;
      outline: none;
      transition: 0.3s;
      font-family: inherit;
    }

    .form-item textarea:focus,
    .form-item input:focus {
      border-color: #b45309;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(60, 122, 49, 0.1);
    }

    .form-grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .form-check {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 15px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #555;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .form-check input {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .luxe-submit-btn {
      align-self: flex-start;
      background: #b45309;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 18px 45px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .luxe-submit-btn:hover {
      background: #b45309;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    /* Grass Divider */
    .grass-divider {
      width: 100%;
      line-height: 0;
      background: #f8f1ec;
      margin-top: -1px;
    }

    .grass-divider svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 80px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 992px) {
      .form-grid-3 {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .hero-content-inner h1 {
        font-size: 2.75rem;
      }
      .comment-area {
        padding: 40px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
